parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Steering Drag Link Failure and Welding Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering drag link can cause the vehicle to lose steering control, leading to accidents or injuries. The welding of the drag link as a repair solution can also lead to further safety issues, such as the inability to align the vehicle, which can cause uneven tire wear and affect vehicle stability.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Repair Solution and Lack of Replacement Parts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate repair solution of welding the drag link can lead to further safety issues, and the lack of replacement parts can cause delays and inconvenience to vehicle owners.
